			["DebloatCheckTip"] = "Writes Microsoft's own group-policy settings into the new Windows to turn off Copilot, the Teams/Chat icon, suggested apps and ads, web search in Start, the advertising ID, and to set telemetry to the minimum. Applied offline to the install image — reversible, installs nothing extra.",
			["AddNetworkDriversCheckTip"] = "Copies this computer's network and Wi-Fi drivers into the new Windows so Wi-Fi appears during first-time setup. Most useful when you will install on the same or a similar PC.",
			["AddAllDriversCheckTip"] = "Copies every third-party driver from this PC into the new Windows (graphics, chipset, audio, network…). Best when installing on the same hardware. Takes longer and uses more space.",
			["HelpTitle"] = "How to use DriveForge",
			["HelpBody"] = "How to use DriveForge — 3 steps\r\n\r\n1) Choose what to make (top-left):\r\n   • \"Create Windows USB\" — install Windows from an ISO you downloaded.\r\n   • \"Clone This PC\" — copy your current Windows onto the drive so it boots exactly like this PC.\r\n\r\n2) Pick the target drive (step 3). Everything on it will be erased. The colored line tells you if the drive is suitable. Your system disk is hidden so you cannot pick it by mistake.\r\n\r\n3) (Optional) Tick options in step 4 — hover any option for an explanation — then press the green button.\r\n\r\nWhen it finishes, plug the drive into the target PC, turn it on, and open the boot menu (usually F12, F9, Esc, or F2 right after power-on) to start from the USB/SSD. The first boot takes a few minutes.\r\n\r\nUse the Diagnostic Center on the right to check a drive's health and speed before using it.\r\n\r\n────────────────────────\r\nDriveForge {0}\r\nFree • Portable (no install) • All features included — no paid tiers.\r\nNo ads. No telemetry. No accounts. Nothing about you is collected or sent anywhere.\r\nWorks offline — the clone engine is built in; only optional downloads (ISOs or the Ventoy engine) use the internet.\r\n\r\nDriveForge is free. To support it, open Settings → Support / Donate. Thank you!",
